text: Friedrich Ostermann (21 June 1932 — 22 October 2018) was a German Roman Catholic official. He was an Auxiliary Bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Münster. Ostermann was born in Münster. He was ordained on 11 February 1958. He resigned in June 2007. Ostermann died in Münster on 22 October 2018.
